<footer class="comment-meta">
<div class="comment-author vcard"><img src="http://0.gravatar.com/avatar/f6e07653015eedb7103ca8666ee732fd?s=50&#038;d=mm&#038;r=pg" width="50" height="50" alt="" class="avatar avatar-50wp-user-avatar wp-user-avatar-50 alignnone photo avatar-default"/><span class="fn"><b>Greycat</b> <br/><a href="http://www.wuxiaworld.com/ti-index/ti-vol-1-chapter-4-1/#comment-355656"><time datetime="2016-05-21T16:07:34+00:00"> May 21, 2016 at 4:07 pm</time></a></span></div> </footer> 
<div class="comment-content">
<p>The Rank B reward he got seemed to be linked to saving the Primary of that movie. Maybe? He did save One, who they were to follow to get it. Might also be altering the plot in a major way. If &#8216;god&#8217; likes watching, watching them deal with an off the rails situation would be more fun.</p>
</div> 
<div class="reply">
<a rel="nofollow" class="comment-reply-login" href="http://www.wuxiaworld.com/wp-login.php?redirect_to=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.wuxiaworld.com%2Fti-index%2Fti-vol-1-chapter-4-1%2F">Log in to Reply</a> <span>&darr;</span> </div> 
